{"timestamp":"2026-03-03T10:41:03.895Z","hookEventName":"PreToolUse","sessionId":"8fbee4ab-d40d-4468-a120-7c2286afff99","transcript_path":"/Users/alexl70/Library/Application Support/Code/User/workspaceStorage/b21d2b2c4133de2eb22354a8d6c6e00a/GitHub.copilot-chat/transcripts/8fbee4ab-d40d-4468-a120-7c2286afff99.jsonl","tool_name":"multi_replace_string_in_file","tool_input":{"explanation":"Add user_name to JWT token and update MVP Provider Registration Flow to allow optional username entry for new users","replacements":[{"filePath":"/Volumes/transcend/src/pet/linkshortener/app_plan.md","oldString":"**Session Management Strategy:**\n\n- All authenticated requests use JWT tokens in `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header\n- JWT tokens include `user_id`, `subject`, `issued_at`, `expiration`\n- No server-side session storage (stateless, scalable)\n- Refresh tokens handled client-side with token rotation","newString":"**Session Management Strategy:**\n\n- All authenticated requests use JWT tokens in `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header\n- JWT tokens include `user_id`, `user_name`, `subject`, `issued_at`, `expiration`\n- No server-side session storage (stateless, scalable)\n- Refresh tokens handled client-side with token rotation"},{"filePath":"/Volumes/transcend/src/pet/linkshortener/app_plan.md","oldString":"**MVP Provider Registration Flow:**\n\n1. Frontend user selects provider (Google, Microsoft, or Facebook)\n2. Frontend redirects to backend `/auth/login/{provider}`\n3. Backend initiates OIDC flow using `go-oidc`\n4. Provider redirects user to login/consent screen\n5. Provider redirects back to `/auth/callback` with authorization code\n6. Backend exchanges code for ID token and user info\n7. Backend checks if user exists in `UserProviders` table:\n   - **Existing user:** Return JWT token\n   - **New user:** Create user in `Users` table with username from provider, create entry in `UserProviders`, return JWT token\n8. Frontend stores JWT token and redirects to dashboard","newString":"**MVP Provider Registration Flow:**\n\n1. Frontend user selects provider (Google, Microsoft, or Facebook)\n2. Frontend redirects to backend `/auth/login/{provider}`\n3. Backend initiates OIDC flow using `go-oidc`\n4. Provider redirects user to login/consent screen\n5. Provider redirects back to `/auth/callback` with authorization code\n6. Backend exchanges code for ID token and user info\n7. Backend checks if user exists in `UserProviders` table:\n   - **Existing user:** Return JWT token with `user_id` and `user_name`\n   - **New user:** Redirect to frontend registration form with provider info pre-filled\n8. Frontend registration form (for new users):\n   - Display suggested username from provider (optional: allow user to customize)\n   - User can optionally enter/modify username or use provider default\n   - Submit to backend `/auth/register` endpoint with chosen username\n9. Backend creates user:\n   - Create user in `Users` table with provided (or default) username\n   - Create entry in `UserProviders` with provider credentials\n   - Return JWT token with `user_id` and `user_name`\n10. Frontend stores JWT token and redirects to dashboard"},{"filePath":"/Volumes/transcend/src/pet/linkshortener/app_plan.md","oldString":"**Future Extension:**\nNew providers (GitHub, Apple, LinkedIn, etc.) can be added by:\n\n- Adding new provider config to backend\n- Adding new login button to frontend\n- No database schema changes required (already supports unlimited providers per user)","newString":"**Username Handling:**\n\n- If user provides custom username during registration: Use provided username (must be unique in `Users` table)\n- If user skips custom username: Use username from OAuth provider (e.g., email prefix, display name)\n- Username can be changed later from user settings/profile page\n\n**Future Extension:**\nNew providers (GitHub, Apple, LinkedIn, etc.) can be added by:\n\n- Adding new provider config to backend\n- Adding new login button to frontend\n- No database schema changes required (already supports unlimited providers per user)"}]},"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HLEkX19AeCxcKyoMLs7U4X__vscode-1772533729888","cwd":"/Volumes/transcend/src/pet/linkshortener"}

